<item>
  <title>PART-TIME TEACHING ASSISTANT, DEPARTMENT OF MARKETING</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/part-time-teaching-assistant-department-marketing</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;PART-TIME TEACHING ASSISTANT, DEPARTMENT OF MARKETING&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;a title="View user profile." href="https://www.ub.bw/user/2371" lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/2371" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" class="username" xml:lang=""&gt;mfetane&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden"&gt;Tue, 22/08/2023 - 08:55&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-department field--type-entity-reference field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Department/Faculty&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Marketing&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-tender-closing-date field--type-datetime field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Closing Date&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Thu, 14 Sep. 2023&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;FACULTY OF BUSINESS - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;DEPARTMENT OF MARKETING&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;VACANCY NO: &lt;span&gt;FOB/MKT&lt;/span&gt; 1/2023 - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;PART-TIME TEACHING ASSISTANT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duties: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidates will be expected to assist with students’ tutorials, practicals, library/internet search, other teaching, learning and research related activities as assigned by the Head of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Department and /or the assigned&lt;span&gt; Academic Staff Members.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Requirements: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants should have a relevant bachelor’s degree with at least a 2.1 pass or better in Marketing, International Business or related qualifications. Preference will be given to those with demonstrable/hands-on knowledge of data analysis using SPSS. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Remuneration: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The University offers competitive part-time rates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;How to Apply:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; Applicants are to address the stated qualification and provide other information to assist the University determine their suitability for the position.  They should also quote the vacancy number of the post applied for, provide current CV’s (including telephone, telefax and email), certified copies of educational certificates and transcripts, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;names and addresses of three referees, and send complete documentation to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;: &lt;strong&gt;The Human Resource Manager, &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;Faculty of Business, University of Botswana, Private Bag UB00701, Gaborone, Botswana, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;Telephone (267) 355 2231 or 355 5844; Email: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:fobvacancies@ub.ac.bw"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;fobvacancies@ub.ac.bw&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; Applicants should inform their referees to: (i) Quote the Vacancy number &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;and&lt;strong&gt; position applied for &lt;/strong&gt;and&lt;strong&gt; (ii) submit their references directly to the above address, before stipulated closing date. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please note that applications with incomplete information shall not be processed. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;Hand delivered applications should be submitted to Block 245 Office 233.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;NB:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing date:  14 September 2023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
