&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;Gaborone, Botswana. &lt;span&gt;Telephone (267) 355 4989; Email: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:fobvacancies@ub.ac.bw"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;fobvacancies@ub.ac.bw&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants should inform their referees to:&lt;strong&gt; i) Quote the Vacancy number and position applied for &lt;/strong&gt;and&lt;strong&gt; ii) submit their references directly to the above address &lt;/strong&gt;before the stipulated closing date. Please note that applications with incomplete information shall not be acknowledged.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt; Hand delivered applications should be submitted to &lt;strong&gt;Block 245, office 236 (245/236). &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

